// B12: a `generated block` body must use the single-string shorthand
// with NO `flow:` keyword. Per design/repair.md a generated block has a
// single-string body and no `flow:` sub-section. An explicit single-
// statement `flow:` body must still fire `G::parse::generated-block-body-shape`.
skill main()
    description: "Demo."
    flow:
        offending_helper()

generated block offending_helper()
    flow:
        "first instruction"
